  "elements": {
    "inscriptions": [
      {
        "id": "insc-2",
        "text": "corridor, but a visible tribute to Victorian engineering. The city’s character is",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -35,
          "y_mm": 688
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-3",
        "text": "These Walls of South Jersey Ironstone",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 20
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -30,
          "y_mm": 387
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "In the spring of 2018, after days of relentless rain, a 100 foot section of this iconic wall",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -8,
          "y_mm": 179
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "collapsed. Though constructed in the mid-1800s as part of a major public works",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -6,
          "y_mm": 114
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-6",
        "text": "project, officials deemed its restoration a private undertaking. The considerable debris",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -6,
          "y_mm": 50
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-7",
        "text": "was then cleared by one man and a wheelbarrow. Design of a stone faced concrete",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 6,
          "y_mm": -10
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "retaining wall with a plan to build it was developed by a friend. Months of community",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 8,
          "y_mm": -72
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "spirited fundraising followed along with two years of construction by immigrants",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -70,
          "y_mm": -138
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "skilled in use of concrete, steel and stone. The man was Edward &apos;Sandy&apos; Feddema,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": -34,
          "y_mm": -200
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "property co-owner. His friend Jeffrey R. Fogg - civil engineer and region native -",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -261
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "managed the project. The two men - both in their seventies - together went on to scour",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -316
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "local sandpits and farms for additional giant ironstones, then lifted, cut, carted, shaped",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -371
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "and placed them to form a new upper wall and constructed new granite gabion baskets",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -426
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "to secure the original stairway. Completed in November 2021, these walls now stand",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 11
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -481
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "testament to an indomitable fellowship, monuments to civic pride and history, and",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -536
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "tribute to the future. To remember them and those who labored with them, generously",
        "font": {
          "family": "Arial",
          "size_mm": 12
        },
        "position": {
          "x_mm": 0,
          "y_mm": -591
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffb35a",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "donated, or cheered this grueling work from the streets, this plaque is set",
